title: Ebro In The Morning - VMA's, the US Open + Remembering 9/11
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
On this episode of Ebro In the Morning - the crew of Ebro, Laura, and Rosenberg discuss the often whacky VMA's, the random celebrities at the US Open, and about the legacy of 9/11. Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments at 12, 44, and 1:12. 

Enjoy Hot 97's flagship program - Ebro In the Morning !
